422 MatrixXd sample_gppath(double unit_intv_len, double* hyp)
423 {
424  MatrixXd rand_paths, mean_path;
425  int nr_path = 100;
426  int nr_pnt = pnts.rows();
427 
428  MatrixXd nr_intvs(nr_pnt - 1, 1);
429  MatrixXd len_abs(nr_pnt - 1, 1);
430  MatrixXd min_intvs(nr_pnt - 1, 1);
431 
432  for (int i = 0; i < nr_pnt - 1; i++)
433  {
434  len_abs(i, 0) = getdist(pnts.row(i), pnts.row(i + 1));
435 
436  nr_intvs(i, 0) = ceil(len_abs(i, 0) / unit_intv_len);
437 
438  if (i == 0)
439  min_intvs(i, 0) = nr_intvs(i, 0);
440  else
441  min_intvs(i, 0) = nr_intvs(i, 0) + min_intvs(i - 1, 0);
442  }
443 
444  MatrixXd test_inputs;
445 
446  test_inputs = linspace(0, len_abs.sum(), nr_intvs.sum());
447 
448  MatrixXd gp_inputs(nr_pnt, 1);
449 
450  for (int i = 0; i < nr_pnt; i++)
451  {
452  if (i == 0)
453  gp_inputs(i, 0) = test_inputs(0, 0);
454  else
455  {
456  int tmp_i = min_intvs(i - 1, 0);
457 
458  if (tmp_i <= 0) tmp_i++;
459 
460  gp_inputs(i, 0) = test_inputs(tmp_i - 1, 0);
461  }
462 
463  }
464 
465  MatrixXd gp_outputs;
466  gp_outputs = pnts;
467 
468  GPRClass GPR(gp_inputs, gp_outputs, hyp);
469 
470  mean_path = GPR.GPRmean(test_inputs);
471 
472  MatrixXd Kpost, R, cR;
473 
474  Kpost = GPR.GPRvar(test_inputs);
475 
476  double var_post = 1e-7;
477 
478  Kpost = Kpost + var_post*MatrixXd::Identity(nr_intvs.sum(), nr_intvs.sum());
479 
480  double len_path = nr_intvs.sum();
481 
482  R = (Kpost + Kpost.transpose()) / 2;
483 
484  LLT<MatrixXd> A_LLT(R);
485  cR = A_LLT.matrixL().transpose();
486 
487  MatrixXd Rmtx = MatrixXd::Random(2 * nr_path, len_path);
488 
489  MatrixXd multi_tmp(Rmtx.rows(), cR.cols());
490 
491  multi_tmp = GPR.Multi(Rmtx, cR);
492 
493  rand_paths = mean_path.transpose().replicate(nr_path, 1);
494 
495  rand_paths = rand_paths + multi_tmp;
496 
497  return rand_paths;
498 }

528 bool isCollision(VectorXd x1, VectorXd x2)
529 {
530  int threshold = 100;
531 
532  Vector2d tmpx1, tmpx2, tmp;
533 
534  tmpx1(0) = x1(0) - robot_pose(0);
535  tmpx1(1) = x1(1) - robot_pose(1);
536 
537  tmpx2(0) = x2(0) - robot_pose(0);
538  tmpx2(1) = x2(1) - robot_pose(1);
539 
540  tmp(0) = tmpx1(0)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) - tmpx1(1)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
541  tmp(1) = tmpx1(0)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) + tmpx1(1)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
542  tmpx1 = tmp;
543 
544  tmp(0) = tmpx2(0)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) - tmpx2(1)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
545  tmp(1) = tmpx2(0)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) + tmpx2(1)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
546  tmpx2 = tmp;
547 
548  int map_x1 = (int)(tmpx1(0) / res + map_origin_x);
549  int map_y1 = (int)(tmpx1(1) / res + map_origin_y);
550  int map_x2 = (int)(tmpx2(0) / res + map_origin_x);
551  int map_y2 = (int)(tmpx2(1) / res + map_origin_y);
552  bool isCol = false;
553 
554  int minx = cv::min(map_x1, map_x2);
555  int maxx = cv::max(map_x1, map_x2);
556  int miny = cv::min(map_y1, map_y2);
557  int maxy = cv::max(map_y1, map_y2);
558 
559  int i, j;
560 
561  for (j = miny; j < maxy + 1; j++)
562  {
563  for (i = minx; i < maxx + 1; i++)
564  {
565  if (map.at<uchar>(i, j) < threshold) isCol = true;
566  }
567  }
568 
569  return isCol;
570 
571 }

573 int calculate_cost(VectorXd x1, VectorXd x2) {
574 
575 
576  int cost = 0;
577  int minimum_cost = 255;
578 
579  Vector2d tmpx1, tmpx2, tmp;
580 
581  tmpx1(0) = x1(0) - robot_pose(0);
582  tmpx1(1) = x1(1) - robot_pose(1);
583 
584  tmpx2(0) = x2(0) - robot_pose(0);
585  tmpx2(1) = x2(1) - robot_pose(1);
586 
587  tmp(0) = tmpx1(0)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) - tmpx1(1)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
588  tmp(1) = tmpx1(0)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) + tmpx1(1)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
589  tmpx1 = tmp;
590 
591  tmp(0) = tmpx2(0)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) - tmpx2(1)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
592  tmp(1) = tmpx2(0)*sin(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI) + tmpx2(1)*cos(-robot_pose(2) + M_PI);
593  tmpx2 = tmp;
594 
595  for (int i = 0; i < intv_num; i++){
596 
597  double x, y;
598 
599  x = tmpx1(0) + (tmpx2(0) - tmpx1(0))*(i + 1) / intv_num;
600  y = tmpx1(1) + (tmpx2(1) - tmpx1(1))*(i + 1) / intv_num;
601 
602  int map_x = (int)(x / res + map_origin_x);
603  int map_y = (int)(y / res + map_origin_y);
604 
605  if(map.at<uchar>(map_x, map_y) < minimum_cost)
606  minimum_cost = map.at<uchar>(map_x, map_y);
607 
608  cost += minimum_cost;
609 
610  }
611 
612  return cost;
613 }
